# Template for local environment variables.
#
# 1. Copy this file to `.env` (which is gitignored and must NEVER be committed).
# 2. Fill in your own LOCAL values.
#
# Real/production secrets live ONLY in the deploy platform's environment store
# (e.g. Vercel) — never in this repo, encrypted or otherwise. See SECURITY.md.
#
# The app is currently a static client-only game and needs no secrets. As it
# grows, document each required key here with a PLACEHOLDER value (never a real
# one), e.g.:
#
# DATABASE_URL=postgres://user:password@host:5432/dbname
# AUTH_SECRET=replace-me
